## Project Structure

```
DeepFake_Studio/
├── main_v1.1.py              ← Main application
├── requirements.txt
├── README.md
├── config.json               ← Saved session config (auto-generated)
├── inswapper_128.onnx        ← InsightFace model
├── GFPGANv1.4.pth            ← Optional face enhancer
├── SimSwap/                  ← git clone neuralchen/SimSwap
├── SadTalker/                ← git clone OpenTalker/SadTalker
├── first-order-model/        ← git clone AliaksandrSiarohin/first-order-model
└── output/                   ← Default output directory
```

