## Toolbar Reference

| Button | Action |
|---|---|
| 🗒 New Session | Clear all inputs, previews and log |
| 📂 Load Config | Restore a saved session from JSON |
| 💾 Save Config | Save current session paths to JSON |
| ⚙️ Settings | Configure temp dir and preview options |
| 🔍 Deps | Open dependency checker with pip install runner |
| ❓ Help | Quick start guide |
| 📋 About | Version and backend info |

